Retain your current details
The left hand column above displays the contact details that we currently hold for you.If you would like these details stay the same, please log into your account on the Dementia Friends website (https://www.dementiafriends.org.uk/login) and reject the changes.

Update your details
If you would like to update your contact details to those displayed in the right hand column above, , please log into your account on the Dementia Friends website (https://www.dementiafriends.org.uk/login) and choose the ‘Accept’ option.

If you have any questions, please email us at DementiaFriends@Alzheimers.org.uk.

